    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Peter Aloysius Harjanto</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"https://id.quora.com/profile/Peter-A-Harjanto\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/e/e4/Peter-aloysius-harjanto.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Peter-aloysius-harjanto.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Peter Aloysius Harjanto <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Peter Aloysius Harjanto</b>, (Peter Alloysius)<br />\nan Indonesian computer scientist, IT professional, chess player and as computer chess programmer author of the free <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a> chess engine <a href=\"/Petir\" title=\"Petir\">Petir</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> . While student at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sekolah_Tinggi_Teknik_Surabaya\">STTS</a> from 2000 until 2004, he represented STTS to win several chess championships in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surabaya\">Surabaya</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_Aloysius_Harjanto&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=354078\">mtd(f) and null move</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Alloysius</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a> March 11, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/MTD(f)\" title=\"MTD(f)\">MTD(f)</a>, <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=355083\">evaluation tuning tricks</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Alloysius</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 17, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=377814\">how to calculate nps?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Alloysius</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 19, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Nodes_per_Second\" title=\"Nodes per Second\">Nodes per Second</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=379100\">negascout and PVS?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Alloysius</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 26, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/NegaScout\" title=\"NegaScout\">NegaScout</a>, <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">Principal Variation Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=388211\">Petir 1.0 is now available</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Peter Alloysius</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 19, 2004</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_Aloysius_Harjanto&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://id.quora.com/profile/Peter-A-Harjanto\">Peter A. Harjanto - Quora</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.quora.com/How-can-computers-play-a-complicated-game-as-chess\">How can computers play a complicated game as chess? - Quora</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://codepeter.wordpress.com/\">Looking from another side</a> Peter's blog (Indonesian)</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://codepeter.wordpress.com/category/computer-chess/\">Computer Chess</a></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Peter_Aloysius_Harjanto&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://id.quora.com/profile/Peter-A-Harjanto\">Peter A. Harjanto - Quora</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://kirill-kryukov.com/chess/kcec/cgi/engine_details.cgi?print=Details&amp;each_game=1&amp;eng=Petir%204.999999\">Petir 4.999999</a> in <a href=\"/KCEC\" title=\"KCEC\">KCEC</a> by <a href=\"/Kirill_Kryukov\" title=\"Kirill Kryukov\">Kirill Kryukov</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Peter Aloysius Harjanto former LinkedIn site</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<